  "loc.input.help.actionOnUnmanageResources": "指定对模板中未定义的资源执行的操作。",
  "loc.input.label.actionOnUnmanageResourceGroups": "对非托管资源组的操作",
  "loc.input.help.actionOnUnmanageResourceGroups": "指定对模板中未定义的资源组执行的操作。",
  "loc.input.label.actionOnUnmanageManagementGroups": "对非托管管理组的操作",
  "loc.input.help.actionOnUnmanageManagementGroups": "指定对模板中未定义的管理组执行的操作。",
  "loc.input.label.denySettingsMode": "拒绝设置模式",
  "loc.input.help.denySettingsMode": "指定拒绝设置的模式，以防止未经授权的更改。",
